    "comment": "Rationale: Using immuno-EM on rat hippoacampal tissue this paper demonstrates that the transmembrane receptor mGluR5 is localized at the periphery of the PSD.\n\n9/3/2017 Pim:\n-Fig 6 show quantitative support for postsynaptic membrane localizition just **outside** of the PSD membrane (so not **inside** the PSD membrane), this choice is bit arbitatry I guess. But I chosse to follow the data in figure 6.\n-Since Fig.6. is on CA1 area of hippocampus I added this info to the synapse type info.\n-\"integral component\" rerived from TM domains of GRM5.. Experimental description: from M&M: \"[...] adult female Wistar rats (200-250 g) were deeply anaesthetized [...]\"",
